            <annotation>
              <subject>http://cdm.ovh/rsm/operations/rope/rope</subject>
              <property>http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/description</property>
              <object>
                <lexicalForm>The RSM Operations ontology is about train operations processes and their participants. It also allows to cover data exchange items (such as telematics messages) as " information objects" in the sense of DUL.

This ontology refers to the DUL upper ontology (DOLCE+DnS Ultralite) which is imported here. Production versions may see the DUL import axiom removed.</lexicalForm>
                <datatype/>
                <language>en</language>
              </object>
            </annotation>
