              <object>
                <lexicalForm>Description that is common to paths, planned journeys, and executed journeys. It has an origin, departure time, destination, arrival time.

It consists in JourneySections, each journey section has the same structure.</lexicalForm>
                <datatype/>
                <language>en</language>
              </object>
