                <lexicalForm>Superclass for all messages exchanged in the context of the FP5 demo. Properties are from PROV-O (emitter, generation time) and full text (string, e.g. JSON snippet). The full text follows a schema not further specified here (TAF XSD or FP5-specific JSON schema, respectively).
