                <lexicalForm>Can be extended to include powered car or trailer roles.
Case of hauled locomotive (fr: marchandise roulante) does not belong here, as no traction is provided.
To be differetiated from (possible, not included) traction provider role, the agent being an organization in that case.</lexicalForm>
