            <annotation>
              <subject>https://cdm.ovh/rsm/operations/rope/rope#Train</subject>
              <property>http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment</property>
              <object>
                <lexicalForm>For want of a better class name: denotes the rolling stock (locos, wagons...) AND their supplies (possibly depleted) AND their (variable) loads, considered as a whole, i.e. whatever is moved somewhere between origin and destination in a Train run.

Not to be confused with the operational concept "Train" (a process), embodied here by class TrainRun.</lexicalForm>
                <datatype/>
                <language>en</language>
              </object>
            </annotation>
          </annotations>
